vgt - Video Trailer Fetcher

USAGE:
    vgt

DESCRIPTION:
    Fetch movie trailers from The Movie Database (TMDB). Gets recent
    movies based on configuration and downloads their trailers.

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-videos-the-movie-database-api-key KEY
        TMDB v3 API key (required)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-genre GENRE
        Genre name or numeric genre ID (default: Action)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-fetch-count NUM
        Max movies to process (default: 50)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-region REGION
        ISO 3166-1 region code (default: US)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-language LANGUAGE
        ISO 639-1 language code (default: en-US)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-days-back DAYS
        Days back for "recently released" (default: 90)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-days-ahead DAYS
        Days ahead for "upcoming" (default: 90)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-min-votes NUM
        Minimum vote count filter (default: 10)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-sort-by SORT
        Sort order (default: primary_release_date.desc)

    -conf-videos-movie-trailer-origin-country COUNTRY
        Origin country filter (default: US)

EXAMPLES:
    vgt
